Puppet module: ant

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages ant
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include ant              # Install and run ant with standard configurations.
include ant::disable     # Disable ant service.
include ant::disableboot # Disable ant service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include ant::absent      # Remove ant package.

DEPENDENCIES:
common::untar-gz 
